-- Komatsu Raises Net Forecast 17% on Mining, Construction Machinery Exports
-- Go Onomitsu
-- 2010-07-13T06:07:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/komatsu-raises-net-forecast-17-on-mining-construction-machinery-exports.html

          
          
             Komatsu Ltd. raised its full-year
net income forecast by 17 percent to 105 billion yen, citing
demand for construction and mining machinery in Asia and Central
and South America. Tokyo-based Komatsu released the new forecast
in a statement to the Tokyo Stock Exchange.  
